	<p pid="a.161.2/1">The Information Centre's workforce data are collected annually and are a snapshot of staff in post as at <phrase class="date" code="">30 September</phrase> each year. The most recent data, provided in the Answer given to the noble Lord on <phrase class="date" code="2007-05-09">9 May</phrase> (<I>Official Report</I>, col. <I>WA</I><I></I><I>264</I>), show the headcount position as at <phrase class="date" code="2006-09-30">30 September 2006</phrase>. Data for 2007 are due for collection on <phrase class="date" code="">30 September 2007</phrase> and although a publication date has not yet been set it is planned to be in the spring of 2008.</p>
</reply>
